&lt;h1&gt;Bolton Together&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Opportunity to support children and young people to Thrive&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experienced and highly skilled in supporting children and young people to improve their emotional health and well-being? Committed to helping children and young people to achieve their goals?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is the opportunity for you….. We have two positions available for you to work collaboratively with partners, young people and families. Join a growing team and play a key role in shaping an innovative service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Emotional Health and Well- Being Practitioner x 2 £23,000 - £26,000 per annum, up to full time hours available (Hours to be agreed with successful applicant) Fixed Term initially for 18 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please refer to the Job Description , Person Specification and recruitment pack for further information.&lt;/p&gt;
